          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px;">We also cover {area.nearby.join(", ")} and surrounding areas. With 20+ years experience serving East London and Essex, we pride ourselves on honest pricing, fast turnaround times, and quality repairs.</p>
