          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 24px;">
            <div><h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">‚ö° Same Day Service</h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Most repairs completed within 24 hours. Emergency same-day service available for {area.name} residents.</p></div>
            <div><h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">üí∑ No Fix, No Fee</h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Free diagnosis on all repairs. If we can't fix your computer, you don't pay. Transparent pricing with no hidden charges.</p></div>
            <div><h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">üöó Free Collection</h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Can't get to us? We'll collect your computer from {area.name} and deliver it back when repaired, completely free.</p></div>
            <div><h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 8px;">üèÜ 20+ Years Experience</h3><p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Trusted by hundreds of customers across {area.region}. Check our 5-star Google reviews from satisfied customers.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="section-bg" style="padding: 60px 0;">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--solar-orange); font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 28px); margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS - {area.name.toUpperCase()}</h2>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px;">
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Do you offer computer repair in Dagenham?</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Yes! We provide full computer and laptop repair services to all Dagenham postcodes including RM8, RM9, and RM10. We offer free collection and delivery throughout Dagenham, Becontree, and surrounding areas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">How much does computer repair cost in Dagenham?</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">We offer competitive fixed prices with free diagnosis. Virus removal starts from ¬£40, screen replacements from ¬£60, and most software repairs from ¬£30. Call us for a free quote on 07971 331814.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">How quickly can you repair my computer?</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Most repairs are completed within 24-48 hours. For urgent repairs, we offer same-day service for Dagenham customers. We're open 7 days a week, 9AM to 9PM.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 24px;">
            <h3 class="space-font" style="color: var(--plasma-cyan); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Do you repair Macs and Apple laptops in Dagenham?</h3>
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">Yes, we repair all computer brands including Apple MacBooks, iMacs, Dell, HP, Lenovo, Asus, Acer, and custom-built PCs. We have experience with both Windows and macOS systems.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
